data.description: Fully remodeled elegance on an oversized corner lot w/ RV parking. This versatile home features a spacious open floor plan, a chef's kitchen with modern tones, high ceilings, solar panels, 3 car garage, 4 bedrooms plus family/office den. Upgrades include newer flooring, kitchen two tone soft close cabinets, new interior and exterior paint, new appliances, updated lighting fixtures & fans, renovated master bathroom with glass shower and garden tub, updated quartz countertops, and wood work accents. The kitchen island was remastered to remove a lifted ledge and become a single level surface with a farmhouse sink. The living room gas fireplace has been elevated with contemporary stone work edging and wood mantel, plus a removed pony wall to naturally open the great room space. The expansive backyard hosts a storage shed, covered storage port, a fenced chicken coup, garden beds, trellises for thornless blackberries, blueberries, boysenberries, raspberries, and numerous fruit trees.  Your sustainability oasis awaits!
